三人在除夕夜演出外的一场车祸中丧生后，他们谈到了他们的“震惊和悲伤”。</p><p> 12月31日，乐队在纽约罗彻斯特的柯达中心演出。</p><p>中午12时50分左右，当约1000人离开会场时，一辆福特Expedition与一辆三菱欧蓝德相撞，两车冲撞了一群行人。</p><p>欧蓝德号上有两人死亡，至少有九人受伤。周二（1月2日）， <a href="https://www.cnn.com/us/live-news/rochester-ny-crash-kodak-center/h_42b9da1b7734147b95002a3b6eb498e0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>CNN</em>报道</a>称，第三人、35岁的迈克尔·艾弗里（Michael Avery）死亡。</p><p>罗彻斯特警方后来说，艾弗里似乎“故意”超速冲向其他车辆和行人，并且他的展览车上装有煤气罐。事故导致火灾，花了一个小时才被扑灭。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1k1-ohMsv7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 53